bilingual.target: 但总体的消息还是令人鼓舞。

bilingual.source: How satisfied are you with our company overall?
bilingual.target: ﹒您对我们公司总体的感觉，请问您是怎样的满意程度？
战略角度:总体的组合商业结果

bilingual.source: The research observe and study the imagery communication psychotherapy overall.
bilingual.target: 本研究对意象对话心理疗法进行了总体的考察。

bilingual.source: This is the overall layout of the buildings have greater impact.
bilingual.target: 这对建筑总体的布局有较大影响。

bilingual.source: After finally finishing the book, my overall impression is a good one.
bilingual.target: 读完这本书，我总体的印象是，这是本好书。

bilingual.source: They show whether the overall bullishness or bearishness is rising or falling.
bilingual.target: 它们表明市场总体的多头或空头是上涨或下跌.

bilingual.source: No reliable and rigorous sampling techniques that the overall reasoning is sheer nonsense.
bilingual.target: 没有可靠和严谨的抽样技术保证，对总体的推断纯属无稽之谈。

bilingual.source: For example, Colorado Springs and Detroit both score an overall opportunity level of 55.
bilingual.target: 举个例子，科罗拉多州的斯普林斯和（密歇根州的）底特律两个城市总体的儿童机会得分都是55分。

bilingual.source: These early results showed no overall association between Actos exposure and risk of bladder cancer.
bilingual.target: 这些早期的结果显示吡格列酮应用与膀胱癌风险之间没有总体的联系。

list.abstract: overall，英 [ˌəʊvərˈɔːl , ˈəʊvərɔːl]，美 [ˌoʊvərˈɔːl , ˈoʊvərɔːl]。英语单词，作形容词时，指的是总的；整体的；包括一切的。作副词时，指的是总的来说；作为整体。作名词时，指的是工作服；防护服；骑马裤。短语搭配为“dressed overall（挂满旗的）”。例句为“The overall facts ought to reassure us.（总的事实应该让我们放心）”。 overall近义词为entire，outright，jeans。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, second in two years. Third overall.
What's this one? "Bulk apperception"? Basically overall intelligence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个是什么？"整体统觉"？基本上就是总体智慧。

yingyinNormal.en: It was, overall, what's the word I'm looking for? Stupid? So stupid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总体来说我该怎么形容呢?蠢，超蠢的。

yingyinNormal.en: You will command overall strategy. Your toon leaders will each command a battle group.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你将控制总体策略，你的小队长们将各领导一个战略小组。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. I think people underestimate the importance of detail to the overall impact. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊。我觉得人们会低估注重细节对整体感觉的影响。是啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Overall wages are on the rise. And that's very welcome news for millions of hardworking Americans.
yingyinNormal.zh: 整体的工资水平在上涨，这是数百万辛勤工作的国人非常欢迎的消息。

yingyinNormal.en: Overall, behaviors that are perceived as being less frequent are also the ones that people tend to weigh more heavily when forming and updating impressions, highly immoral actions and highly competent actions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总的来说，在形成以及更新印象时，人们对不太常出现的行为，印象会比较深刻，或是非常不道德的行为，还有非常令人满意的行为的时候。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Rather than obsessing over the scale, turn your focus to how you look, feel, how your clothes fit and your <highlight>overall</highlight> energy level.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与其纠结于体重秤，不如将你的注意力转移到你的外表、感觉、衣服的合身程度以及你的整体精力水平上。

examination_example.sentence: That was bad to my <highlight>overall</highlight> fitness goals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这对我的整体健康目标很不利。

examination_example.sentence: Together, they make up the reading component of your <highlight>overall</highlight> literacy, or relationship to your surrounding textual environment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它们共同构成了你整体读写能力的阅读部分，或与你周围文本环境的关系。

examination_example.sentence: It's worth noting that the <highlight>overall</highlight> share of young adults living with their parents was not at a record high in 2014.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 值得一提的是，2014年和父母住在一起的年轻人总占比并非史上最高。

examination_example.sentence: They found that, <highlight>overall</highlight>, 31% of marriages ended in divorce over the period studied.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 总的来说，他们发现，在研究期间，31%的婚姻以离婚告终。

examination_example.sentence: While cohabitation (同居) has been on the rise, the <highlight>overall</highlight> share of young adults either married or living with an unmarried partner has substantially fallen since 1990.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然同居现象一直在增加，但自1990年以来，已婚或与未婚伴侣同居的年轻人的总体比例大幅下降。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>overall</highlight> number of bacteria on the surface mattered more, and this decreased over time after the initial introduction.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 表面的细菌总数更重要，而且在最初引入后，随着时间的推移，细菌数量会减少。

examination_example.sentence: Those shifts have yet to be reflected in record obesity levels, which stand at 36.5% <highlight>overall</highlight> in the US.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些转变尚未反映在创纪录的肥胖水平中，美国的肥胖率大体上为36.5%。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The <highlight>overall</highlight> effects of the publicity have been more beneficial than harmful.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 宣传的总体效果是利大于弊。

examination_example.sentence: The implications of music on <highlight>overall</highlight> well-being are really impressive.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 音乐对整体幸福感的影响确实令人印象深刻。

examination_example.sentence: Your applications should be carefully prepared in order that the school you like can have an <highlight>overall</highlight> and accurate konwledge of your abilities.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你应该仔细准备的申请书，这样你喜欢的学校才能对你的能力有一个全面而准确的了解。
